# Coin toss minigame



Two-slot coin flip to choose between two movie candidates (or a mystery pick).



## Entry flow



1. `buildCoinTossUI` — constructs slot UI and wires events

2. `armCoinToss` — arms flip after slots are filled

3. `launchCoinToss` — runs the flip sequence

4. `runCoinTossSpinSequence` — blip-synced visual flip segments



## Movie pool



Uses `buildFilteredCoinTossPool` — same category/runtime/decade/watched filters as ticket shuffle.



Mystery pick: `pickMysteryFlickForCoinToss` fills a slot from the filtered pool.



## Blip-synced flip



Flip duration segments are derived from `coin-flip-blip-map.js` (regenerated by `npm run refresh-audio`).



Coin flip bed clips configured in `scripts/audio-paths.mjs` under `coinFlipSpinBedClips`.



After audio path or blip changes, run `npm run refresh-audio`.



## Keeper interaction



`coinTossWouldNeedKeeperSlot` checks if the winner needs a keeper slot. Respect keeper deck full state before allowing flip.
